metadata.name: Scream at 6 am
metadata.description:
Enduring more than a hundred days of fear, pressure and personal and social stress, and seeing killing, torture and threats, and being interrogated for 5 hours...
But at 6 o'clock in the morning of 7 January , when I heard the news of the execution of two innocent youths, I was filled with hatred and a cry as big as the size of the world inside my chest...
